      "text": "Web Pages\n            uniqueId (PK)\n            Status: CRAWLING|INGESTING|PARSING|EXTRACTING|PERSISTING|CRAWLED\n            LastContentModifiedTimestamp (From CURLing the website)\n            LastCrawlTime (System Time when last crawled)\n            frequencyToCheck (Kind of exponential backoff to crawl again - multiple crawls)\n            S3Link\n            Domain_id\n            URL\n\n\n      ",
